song.title: A Shrubbery
song.info:
Winner of the multichannel music compo at Marast 2005.
Have you come to arrange a holiday, or would you like a blow-job? We want a shrubbery! A shrubbery! Nobody expects the Spanish Inquisition! ...blow-job. We want... a blow-job. And now for something completely different. A shrubbery! Another shrubbery-y-y-y...! A shrubbery! Nobody expects... another shrubbery-y-y-y...! A shrubbery!
